<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Elimina Account – BudgetCoach</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:        #0D0D0F;
      --bg-card:   #111118;
      --border:    #2A2A2E;
      --blue:      #4F6EF7;
      --blue-light:#A8B8FF;
      --white:     #F0F0F2;
      --gray:      #888888;
      --gray-dark: #555555;
      --red:       #E24B4A;
      --green:     #22C78A;
      --radius-sm: 8px;
      --radius-md: 10px;
      --radius-lg: 14px;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 48px 16px 64px;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #131320;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--blue);
    }
    .header-text h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .header-text p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--gray);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* Cards */
    .card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .card-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-dark);
      letter-spacing: 0.7px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    /* Steps */
    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .step-num {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #1A1A28;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--blue);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .step-body strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .step-body span {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--gray);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Data table */
    .data-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .data-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .data-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--white);
    }
    .badge {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .badge-delete {
      background: rgba(226, 75, 74, 0.15);
      color: var(--red);
    }
    .badge-keep {
      background: rgba(34, 199, 138, 0.12);
      color: var(--green);
    }

    /* Contact box */
    .contact-card {
      background: rgba(79, 110, 247, 0.07);
      border: 0.5px solid rgba(79, 110, 247, 0.3);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .contact-card .card-label { color: var(--blue-light); }
    .contact-card p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--gray);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .contact-card a {
      color: var(--blue-light);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .contact-card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Warning */
    .warning {
      background: rgba(226, 75, 74, 0.07);
      border: 0.5px solid rgba(226, 75, 74, 0.25);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .warning-icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .warning p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--gray);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .warning strong { color: var(--red); }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--gray-dark);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    footer a {
      color: var(--gray);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">B</div>
      <div class="header-text">
        <h1>BudgetCoach</h1>
        <p>Eliminazione account e dati</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="card">
      <p class="card-label">Come eliminare l'account</p>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>Apri BudgetCoach</strong>
          <span>Avvia l'app sul tuo dispositivo Android e accedi con il tuo account.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>Vai alla scheda Profilo</strong>
          <span>Tocca l'icona Profilo in basso a destra nella barra di navigazione.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>Scorri fino in fondo</strong>
          <span>Scorri verso il basso fino a trovare il pulsante rosso <em>Elimina Account</em>.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <strong>Conferma l'eliminazione</strong>
          <span>Tocca <em>Elimina Account</em> nella finestra di conferma. L'account verrà rimosso immediatamente e verrai disconnesso.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Data deleted/kept -->
    <div class="card">
      <p class="card-label">Dati eliminati e conservati</p>

      <div class="data-row">
        <span class="data-name">Profilo utente (nome, email)</span>
        <span class="badge badge-delete">Eliminato</span>
      </div>
      <div class="data-row">
        <span class="data-name">Spese e transazioni inserite</span>
        <span class="badge badge-delete">Eliminato</span>
      </div>
      <div class="data-row">
        <span class="data-name">Impostazioni budget e obiettivi</span>
        <span class="badge badge-delete">Eliminato</span>
      </div>
      <div class="data-row">
        <span class="data-name">Cronologia chat con AI Coach</span>
        <span class="badge badge-delete">Eliminato</span>
      </div>
      <div class="data-row">
        <span class="data-name">Preferenze di notifica</span>
        <span class="badge badge-delete">Eliminato</span>
      </div>
      <div class="data-row">
        <span class="data-name">Log di sistema anonimi (crash)</span>
        <span class="badge badge-keep">Conservato 90 gg</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Alternative contact -->
    <div class="contact-card">
      <p class="card-label">Non riesci ad accedere all'app?</p>
      <p>
        Se non puoi accedere al tuo account, puoi richiedere la cancellazione via email.
        Scrivi a <a href="mailto:valerio.martori@digitouch.it">valerio.martori@digitouch.it</a>
        con oggetto <strong style="color: var(--white);">"Richiesta eliminazione account"</strong>
        indicando l'indirizzo email associato al tuo account.<br><br>
        La richiesta verrà evasa entro <strong style="color: var(--white);">30 giorni</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Warning -->
    <div class="warning">
      <span class="warning-icon">⚠</span>
      <p>
        <strong>Attenzione:</strong> l'eliminazione dell'account è irreversibile.
        Tutti i tuoi dati verranno rimossi definitivamente e non sarà possibile recuperarli.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <p>BudgetCoach &mdash; sviluppato da Valerio Martori</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 6px;">
        <a href="mailto:valerio.martori@digitouch.it">valerio.martori@digitouch.it</a>
      </p>
    </footer>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
